t-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:楷体">习近平总书记视察江中集团</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b87aaa5282.png" title="594b87aaa5282.png" alt="blob.png"/><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:楷体">习总书记视察后作重要讲话</span></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">6月21日，应江西省山东商会会长董奇之邀，湖北省山东商会长、湖北精英盛华信息科技股份有限公司董事长李文帅，四川省山东商会会长韩东，西藏山东商会会长赵世宏，贵州省山东商会会长刘世军，辽宁省山东商会会长李大利，河北省山东商会会长闫国华，内蒙古山东商会会长郭建军，浙江省山东商会会长刘旭刚，江苏省山东商会会长鲁宏振，山西省山东商会会长伊纪余，湖南省山东商会会长李涛，香港山东商会联合总会名誉会长、澳门山东商会荣誉会长、丝绸之路总商会（美国）荣誉会长、山东人杂志社社长曲玉国齐聚江西南昌，参观了江中集团制造基地——江中药谷。江中药谷位于南昌市近郊的湾里，占地3000亩，四周森林覆盖，内有湖泊环绕，自然空气洁净度达到30万级。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:28px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b8777d8235.png" title="594b8777d8235.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:楷体">山东商会会长参观江中集团</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b8782c3b1b.png" title="594b8782c3b1b.png" alt="blob.png"/>&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:26px;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b8789b5608.png" title="594b8789b5608.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b879203594.png" title="594b879203594.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b879965898.png" title="594b879965898.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">2016年2月3日，习近平总书记莅临江中药谷。习总书记察看产品展示、视察自动化生产线和质量检测中心，并听取江西省生物医药产业发展总体情况介绍，对江中集团给予了充分肯定。习总书记视察后即兴作重要讲话，并指出：“中医药是中华民族的瑰宝，一定要保护好、发掘好、发展好、传承好，所有制药企业都要增强质量意识、社会责任意识，努力研制和生产质优价廉、疗效好的药品，坚决杜绝假冒伪劣，为推进全体健康多作贡献。你们这个企业的发展，我能看到未来有更加光明的前景。祝你们再接再厉，新的一年更上一层楼。”&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b874b8db41.png" title="594b874b8db41.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 楷体;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:楷体">江中药谷实景（局部）</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20170622594b873dcd007.png" title="594b873dcd007.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 150%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">江西江中制药（集团）有限责任公司是省属国有大型中药制药企业，江中集团出身于江西中医学院的校办企业，有着42年的中药科研与生产的历史，在国内有很高的知名度和美誉度。历经40余年的发展，江中制药现已成长为一家集医药制造、保健食品、功能食品于一体的控股一家上市公司的现代化企业集团。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = null, top = 0, create_id = 12, create_time = '2017-11-27 11:53:36.0', article_time = '2017-06-21 00:00:00.0', status = 2, sort = 6, top_title = '精信科技董事长李文帅应邀参观江中集团制造基地——江中药谷', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 75;
