ng SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; line-height: 24px; background: white;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 0.1px; font-size: 20px;">李文帅董事长陪同区领导参观了总部办公楼，并在座谈会上对公司的防疫措施和复工复产情况进行了详细汇报。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; line-height: 25px;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 0.1px;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 41px; line-height: 25px;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 0.1px;">公司武汉总部于3月30日正式复工，复工期间，公司</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;">出台了<span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60);">复工防控方案，成立了复工防控领导小组，严格执行防疫措施，办公场所每日多次消毒；复工人员每日检查健康绿码，测量体温并登记在册；复工及来访人员对手部、衣物、鞋底进行消毒后方可进入办公场所。公司对员工用餐时间、上下班时间实行分批错峰制，工位保持最大间隔，严防人员群聚。在机制化的严防严控下，公司做到了全体员工零感染，复工复产也正有条不紊地进行中。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; cle