ing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区委常委、区委统战部部长潘利国，副部长杨丽、周呈斌</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">与公司管理层进行了全面而深入的交流。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">总裁助理杨植圣</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">对</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">市</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">委统战部的关怀和支持再次表示了衷心的感谢。座谈会在愉快的氛围中圆满结束。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = '50', top = 1, create_id = 12, create_time = '2021-02-20 15:12:09.0', article_time = '2020-07-18 00:00:00.0', status = 2, sort = 1, top_title = '武汉市委统战部副部长，市工商联党组书记耿洪山一行走访精信科技调研复工复产情况', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 194;
