rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财年第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、第二</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季经营分析会于咸宁举行。来自全国各地的精信精英齐聚一堂，就</span>20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财年第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、第二</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季各个部门的重点工作进行了总结和分享，并对第</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季的工作计划和目标进行了部署。本次会议内容丰富、重点突出、高效务实</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52c8e668a4.png" title="5fa52c8e668a4.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="text-indent: 36px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">培训课程《团队管理</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">40条军规</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">》中拉开帷幕，经过三个多小时的认真学习，各部门与会人员收获了宝贵的团队管理知识，受益匪浅。</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52c9a7d61d.png" title="5fa52c9a7d61d.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">次日，业务外包部蔡靖茹、人力资源部王梅、总裁办（企业发展部）光兴、营销部任梦荣、个人和商企</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">通信</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">业务部恩施营服中心赖小宁、徐辉、个人和商企</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">通信</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">业务部黄冈营服中心钟芬、校园通信业务部姜卫代表部门主动出击，迎战主持人</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">竞聘</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。八位</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">选手都表现出了强大的舞台掌控力</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">临场反应力和多维度的才能，逻辑严谨的思辨能力和稳健的台风给大家留下了深刻的印象。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">经过一番</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">激烈的角逐，评委们公平公正的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">评分</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，来自</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">总裁办（企业发展部）的光兴</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">脱颖而出，当选为</span>20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财年第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、第二</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季经营分析会的主持人。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52ca37b7c5.png" title="5fa52ca37b7c5.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本次财季会每天清晨，全体参会人员都会在庄严肃穆的国歌合唱</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">和</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">鼓舞士气</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">《</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">狼道</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">》晨</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">读之后</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，正式开始一天的议程。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52cada1bf9.png" title="5fa52cada1bf9.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52cb6ce8fd.png" title="5fa52cb6ce8fd.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52cc434be9.png" title="5fa52cc434be9.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top:20px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会上，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">增值业务部北京办、河南办、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">重庆</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">办；业务外包部；人力资源部；个人和商企通信业务部武汉营服中心、黄冈营服中心、恩施营服中心；</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">营销部；</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">校园通信业务部等营服部门和职能支撑部门依次上台，详细汇报了第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、第二</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季工作的总结和未来的工作规划，参会人员踊跃对各部门代表进行了提问</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。与会人员还纷纷对新成立部门</span>——营销部的同事表示了热烈欢迎</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d3842fb4.png" title="5fa52d3842fb4.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d423bf51.png" title="5fa52d423bf51.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d5b36488.png" title="5fa52d5b36488.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d6845ece.png" title="5fa52d6845ece.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; text-indent: 36px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d7a1038e.png" title="5fa52d7a1038e.png" alt="image.png"/></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d8839bbf.png" title="5fa52d8839bbf.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52d925c3f4.png" title="5fa52d925c3f4.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司总裁李文帅</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">就团队管理、业务破冰、企业文化在实际工作中的运用进行了详尽的阐述和讲解，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">对各部门汇报内容逐一进行了点评，总结了过去</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">两个</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季公司的成长与不足，并勾勒出下一财季公司发展的方向。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">2020财年以来，国内经济受疫情影响，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">虽然渡过了非常困难的一段时期，但是公司每个部门都在努力的攻坚克难，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:宋体">各营服单元在业务发展上都有新的突破。公司上下一心</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，共克时艰，士气和凝聚力不减反增、越战越勇，为实现全财年的经营计划做好了充分准备。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">增值业务部重点保收入，控制成本费用</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，努力在现有业务的基础上扩张市场，开发新业务，寻找新的利润增长点</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个人和商企通信业务部在不断拓展业务新模式及异业合作项目，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">加强了营收的提升</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">保持了较好的市场占有率</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。李总还</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">高度赞许了恩施营服中心，呼吁各部门的同事可以去恩施实地考察，感受团队氛围，学习先进经验。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">校园通信业务部受疫情影响较大，但秋季迎新整体发展</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">很</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">好，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:宋体">发展量比去年同期有所提升，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">部分学校拥</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">有较</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">高</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的市场占有率。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">业务外包部一直稳定发展，积极与合作方进行紧密的交流和沟通，勇于发现新机遇，开拓新市场。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">营销部是公司今年成立不久的新部门，现在已经在扩展新业务方面积极开疆拓土、大展拳脚，相信在不久后一定会大有可为、未来可期。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">人力资源部持续的为公司引入人才，制定和完善了各项人力制度及各项机制。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">行政部在疫情期间为公司采购了各种防疫物资，做好了每日的防控工作，为疫情期间的安全办公提供了有力保障。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财务部在资金管理方面一直给予各个营服部门大力支撑；在融资方面为公司业务发展提供了坚实的后盾。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">技术部建立、维护和优化的公司各项产品，为公司各部门提供了扎实的技术支持。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">总裁办（企业发展部）在疫情期间梳理了各项惠企政策并且积极与各个落地部门保持沟通，跟进落实情况。对内支撑各个部门，对外也有若干新项目正在顺利进行。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">李总</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">强调</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">，</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">发展是硬道理，增收是主旋律——这是在后疫情时代里</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">我们的第一要务。精信科技全体员工现在不畏艰难、士气高昂，正是公司发展的大好时机，因此我们更要</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">多学习、多思考，围绕着“如何发展、如何增收、如何落地”三个重点</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">高效</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">开展工作。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">会议期间</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">，</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">公司</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">组织</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">大家</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">一起参加</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">了</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">体育锻炼活动，参会人员</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">分成篮球和徒步跑步两个小组。</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">有人</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">开展</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">了</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">激烈的</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">篮球</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">比</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">赛，也有人进行了</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">两小时</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">的</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">徒步跑步运动</span><span style="text-indent: 36px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); letter-spacing: 1px;">。精信伙伴们纷纷在运动场上挥洒着汗水，充分践行了前行成长，全力以赴的个人拼搏精神。</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52dc308991.png" title="5fa52dc308991.png" alt="image.png"/></span><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52dcceb116.png" title="5fa52dcceb116.png" alt="image.png" style="color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px;"/></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议后半程，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">全体参会人员来到武汉总部，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在李总的主持下，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">大家就</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">个人和商企通信业务部武汉营服中心</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">魏松提出的问题</span>——</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">“初次拜访大客户要做好哪些准备”为主题进行全员生发</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。大家运用平时学习积累的知识，结合实际工作和现实案例，每个人对问题作出了三个回答，全员积极讨论，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">提出了</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">许多</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">宝贵的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">真知灼见</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52de362abc.png" title="5fa52de362abc.png" alt="image.png"/><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 36px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">大家分享经验、积极交流、真抓实干、锐意进取。李总认真听取和记录了每一条意见和建议，时而和大家互动、点评</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一次次精彩又务实的思想碰撞和深度研讨，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在会议过程中开花结果，形成了一份具有指导意义的</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">实操方案</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">使全体参会人员都获益良多。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52df2e2cc0.png" title="5fa52df2e2cc0.png" alt="image.png"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><img src="/Uploads/image/202011065fa52df9edffb.png" title="5fa52df9edffb.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 20px 0 0;text-indent: 18px;padding: 0;line-height: 150%;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">在意犹未尽的学习氛围中</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，精信科技</span>20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财年第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、第二</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">财季经营分析会</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">圆满结束，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">精信人</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">再次</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">厉兵秣马，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">用知识和经验武装自己，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(60, 60, 60);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">雷厉风行地投入到了全新的工作中。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 18px; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 150%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;"><span style="color:#3c3c3c"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span></span>疫情打不垮团结奋进、士气如虹的精信人，精信科技必将在李总的带领下逆流而上，不断创造全新的辉煌！</span></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = '52', top = 1, create_id = 12, create_time = '2021-02-20 15:12:42.0', article_time = '2020-11-02 18:00:00.0', status = 2, sort = 1, top_title = '2020财年第一、第二财季经营分析会圆满召开', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 198;
UPDATE jxkj_db.article SET name = '精信科技总裁李文帅参加湖北省第十三届人民代表大会第五次会议', abstract = '1月24日至27日，湖北省第十三届人民代表大会第五次会议在武昌洪山礼堂隆重举行。李总参加会议，为湖北省发展建言献策。', content = '<p style="text-indent:28px;text-align:center"><br/></p><p style="text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; "><span style="text-align: center; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: center; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">1月24日至27日，湖北省第十三届人民代表大会第五次会议在武昌洪山礼堂隆重举行。湖北精英盛华信息科技股份有限公司总裁李文帅参加会议，履行省人大代表职责，为</span><span style="text-align: center; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">湖北省发展建言献策。&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0px;"><img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030a935af0a7.png" title="6030a935af0a7.png" alt="image.png" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030a9452c5d4.png" title="6030a9452c5d4.png" alt="image.png" style="text-align: center;"/><span style="text-align: center; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">开幕大会由湖北省委书记、省人大常委会主任应勇主持。会上，省长王晓东代表省人民政府向大会作政府工作报告。省人大常委会副主任王玲向大会作省人大常委会工作报告。省高级人民法院院长游劝荣向大会作省高级人民法院工作报告。省人民检察院检察长王晋向大会作省人民检察院工作报告。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030a98476e39.png" title="6030a98476e39.png" alt="image.png"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">李总参与武汉代表团审议，听取应勇书记审议发言，并与程用文、庄丹、彭浩、朱敦尧、蒋再秋、胡明荣、李丰、赖春临、叶红、胡丹、王忠林等代表就优化民营经济发展环境、增强科技创新能力等议题展开讨论交流。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030a99022203.png" title="6030a99022203.png" alt="image.png"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0px; "><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;李总在发言中对</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">疫情过后</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">许多</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">民营企业</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">遇到的</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">困难</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">和</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">现状</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">进行了总结</span><span style="text-indent: 37px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 19px;">：</span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">1、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">人才及科技资源获取不足，创新发展受限。</span></span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">2、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">金融资源匹配不够，融资难，融资贵问题，虽有缓解但仍然非常明显。</span></span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">3、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">社会资源匮乏，要素市场不够有序充分，隐形的不公平待遇依然存在。</span></span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">4、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">国际形式严峻复杂，经济下行周期以及新旧动能转化形成的压力很大。</span></span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">5、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">部分行业税费等运行成本高，负担较重，现在经营举步维艰。</span></span></p><p style=";vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">6、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">法律制度不够及时，监管尺度边界模糊，部分企业主对财产安全心理恐慌。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">&nbsp; 李</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">总</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">还对缓解民营企业发展，促进湖北省经济高质量发展提出了若干建设性建议：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">1、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">优化民营经济发展环境，构建亲清政商关系，完善产权制度，依法平等保护民营企业产权和企业家权益。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">2、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">加大对民营企业尤其是科创高新企业的金融支持（在贷款贴息、执行基准贷款利率、贷款年限放宽等方面），银行应有一定比例的贷款贷给民营企业。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">3、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">2021年继续执行社保补贴，优化税收结构，支持高新企业进一步减税降费。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;vertical-align: baseline;line-height: 150%"><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px">4、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">各市州及县市区尽快成立</span>&quot;四不像&quot;科研机构，加快科研成果的转化落地，加速创新驱动实现高质量发展。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">应勇书记仔细听取各与会代表的建言。会议期间，各位代表牢记使命、依法履职、共谋发展，体现了强烈的责任担当和良好的精神风貌。会议审议批准了政府工作报告、</span>“十四五”规划纲要等文件，顺利完成了选举任务。大会于27日圆满闭幕，这次会议，是一次民主团结、凝心聚力、求实奋进的大会。会议取得的各项成果，凝聚了全体代表的智慧，反映了全省人民的共同意愿，必将激励全省上下为开局“十四五”、开启新征程而不懈奋斗。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体"> 在这</span>“挑战前所未有，斗争艰苦卓绝”的一年，李总认真履行省人大代表职责，在会上为湖北民营企业经济发展献计献策，以实际行动当好了人民群众的忠实代表。这既是李总的光荣，也是精信科技全体员工的荣耀。在李总的带领下，精信科技必将蒸蒸日上，再创辉煌！</span></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = '53', top = 1, create_id = 12, create_time = '2021-02-20 15:12:53.0', article_time = '2021-01-27 18:00:00.0', status = 2, sort = 1, top_title = '李总参加湖北省第十三届人民代表大会第五次会议', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 199;
UPDATE jxkj_db.article SET name = '牛年鸿运，开工大吉——李文帅董事长携公司高管派发开工红包', abstract = '开年大吉，牛气冲天！正月初八，精信科技迎来年后的第一个工作日，李总携公司高管为到岗全体员工派发开门红包。', content = '<p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></strong><br/></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">开年大吉，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">牛气冲天</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">！</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; text-align: left;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月初八，精信科技迎来年后的第一</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">个工作日</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span> “新年好”</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">问候声不绝于耳，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">灿烂的笑容</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">如花般绽放。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030b2f782211.png" title="6030b2f782211.png" alt="image.png" style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;"/><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">晨学早课开始前，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司总裁李文帅携</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">公司高管依次来到每个晨学小组，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:1