span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">鼓舞</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">大家节后调整好工作状态和精神面貌，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">全力以赴、好整以暇地投入到工作中，迎战</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">20</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">21</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">乘风破浪，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">扬帆起航。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/image/202102206030b3745b96a.png" title="6030b3745b96a.png" alt="image.png"/><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">新春新开局，奋斗正当时。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">奋发努力才不负美好</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">韶华！</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2021，</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">让我们发扬牛劲牛力，不用扬鞭自奋蹄，鼓足干劲犇起来！</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">新的一年，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">祝</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">精信科技红红火火，再创辉煌！</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">祝</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">所有精信人</spa