verflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"/></strong></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 252, 255); letter-spacing: 0.5px; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible;">团队破冰，增进感情提升凝聚力‍&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 252, 255); visibility: visible;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible;">&nbsp;</strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; visibility: visible;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: Calibri; visibility: visible;">3<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 宋体; visibility: visible;">月</span>31<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 宋体; visibility: visible;">日晚，开班典礼正式启动。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; visibility: visible;">首先大家一起学习了《机制歌》颂唱，接下来通过抽签的方式将参加培训的学员进行分组，通过你来比划我来猜、歌词接龙、演讲辩论三个游戏环节，现场进行班委<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Calibri; visibility: visible;">PK</span>，三轮游戏不仅给予了队员充分展示自己才华的机会，同时也通过团队合作，协同作战的方式，加深了彼此的认识，提升了队员之间凝聚力。</span></span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7dfb9f89e.png" title="624f7dfb9f89e.png" alt="2.png" width="1007" height="665" style="width: 1007px; height: 665px;"/></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; visibility: visible;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; visibility: visible;">在演讲辩论环节，大家围绕“如果你是老板，在孙悟空、猪八戒和沙僧中你会选择谁做你的员工”的主题，展开激烈的辩论，他们</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible;">分别代表了三种不同类型的员工，都有各自的优缺点，只有“知人善用，用人为长”，才能将不同类型员工的价值和潜力发挥出来。通过此次辩论主题，让新员工明白，在团队中只有明确自己的特长和价值，找准自己定位和目标，做到扬长避短，才能更好地实现自己的个人价值。同时通过辩论的方式让新员工懂得，“</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Calibri;">1+1&gt;2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;">”的团队价值，以及“胜则举杯相庆，败则拼死相救”的团队精神。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体;">经过激烈的竞争和精彩的辩论，运营部武汉营服中心销售经理张健胜出，被选为班长，财务部总经理陈维斯被选为学习委员，总裁办（企发部）企宣刘婷被选为纪律委员。总裁助理、人力行政部总经理王靖鑫对成功竞选的班委表示祝贺，为本期的班委进行了授旗仪式，并为所有参加竞选的人员颁发了礼品。</span></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7e041ca1a.png" title="624f7e041ca1a.png" alt="3.png" width="969" height="704" style="width: 969px; height: 704px;"/></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(0, 252, 255); letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em;">传道授业，深度解读企业文化</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 252, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em;"></strong></p><p></p><section data-id="22386" powered-by="xmyeditor.com" data-md5="6a077" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体;">优秀的企业文化不仅有利于凝聚企业的向心力，也可以帮助员工提高自身的文化素养、道德水准。公司董事长李文帅立足于公司的企业文化，从公司的发展目标，岗位工作要求和员工关怀等方面进行了企业文化解读。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">李文帅<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">董事长</span></span>表示精信科技要实现“中国民营百强企业”的目标，首先要做到以“客户为中心”，“客户就是上帝”，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">多站在客户的角度考虑问题，</span>对客户负责，让客户满意，让客户感动，才能保持长久的合作。同时要心怀敬畏之心，切忌“投机取巧，弄虚作假”，无论是对待客户，还是对待员工，只有做到“已所不欲，勿施于人”，才能“走的稳，走的远”。</span></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7e0f89424.png" title="624f7e0f89424.png" alt="4.png" width="970" height="665" style="width: 970px; height: 665px;"/></span></span></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">李文帅<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">董事长</span></span>对新员工<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">岗位工作</span>提出了具体要求。第一，要<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">摆正</span>心态，始终与公司立场保持统一，“与公司同心同德”，为共同的目标努力奋斗。第二，工作方法要科学，工作要<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“</span>重价值、重业绩、重结果</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">”</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体;">，重“功劳”而非“苦劳”，做到“听话、出活”，同时要学会顺瓜摸藤、未雨绸缪、事前推演、事后复盘的工作方法，只有这样才能创造工作价值，提升工作效率。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 