an><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">既然大家选择了精信科技，就需要有“大树”的精神，成为一个大树的第一个条件就是“时间”，“十年树人，百年树木”，要想成功，一定要给自己时间去等待，去经历，去体验，去积累和延伸。</span></span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7ea0a3a71.jpg" title="624f7ea0a3a71.jpg" alt="6.jpg" width="982" height="659" style="width: 982px; height: 659px;"/></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">总裁助理兼运营部CEO李玎为学员带来了运营部校园通信网络建设业务的课程。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">李玎</span>重点介绍了智慧校园业务项目，智慧校园依托大数据云计算，通过感知行为分析能够为校方进行智能化校园管理提供便捷，市场应用前景良好。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">同时他也对产品延伸进行了探讨，例如在为校方提供产品服务的时候，如何依托大数据平台将资源进行整合，如何通过消费行为习惯的培养将流量进行二次变现等。通过<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">李玎</span>深入的介绍，让学员们不仅对校园网的运营模式了解透彻，对精信科技业务转型升级以及未来发展方向也有了信心。</span></span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7eb498f63.png" title="624f7eb498f63.png" alt="7.png" width="991" height="604" style="width: 991px; height: 604px;"/></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">总裁助理兼运营部总经理杨植圣为学员介绍了运营部人力资源服务外包业务。人力资源服务外包业务是公司业务向外的延伸和拓展，精信科技在整合资源的基础上，倡导多元化的发展方式。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">杨植圣</span>说到各位学员作为新的血液加入公司，希望你们可以从自己的专业角度，结合公司现有的资源，发挥自己的才智，带着创新和多元化的思维开展工作，为公司创造价值的同时，实现自己人生价值。</span></span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7eca5b0f0.png" title="624f7eca5b0f0.png" alt="8.png" width="1007" height="626" style="width: 1007px; height: 626px;"/></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;">总裁助理兼人力行政部总经理王靖鑫进行了公司员工手册制度的宣贯。通过制度宣贯让新员工了解公司鼓励什么，摒弃什么。同时也分享了自己工作多年的经验和心得，她强调工作应该由易到难，首先从容易处开刀，先主后次，优先专注处理工作价值高的重要工作；其次要学会抗干扰、定时间，零存整取，集中处理琐碎的事情，学会按流程进行工作，不断优化流程、程序和方法，善用工具，让工作变得简单一些；再次，关键事件逆向复盘找原因，从错误和失败中学习，把握工作的节奏，把工作汇报当成面向客户的产品交付；最后，她希望大家做一个“会做事、好合作、善学习”的精信人，把自己打造成为一个“榜样、担当、成长”的优秀员工。</span></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7ee7107d1.png" title="624f7ee7107d1.png" alt="9.png" width="997" height="667" style="width: 997px; height: 667px;"/></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-indent: 29px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">此次培训还特别安排了一堂宝藏课程——武大营销管理学习分享会，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">市场拓展部</span>副总经理祁欢、运营部鄂东营服中心CEO刘跃艺、运营部综合管理中心主任彭汉兰，他们从武汉大学营销管理培训班结业，现在面向全体员工倾情分享自己的学习成果。祁欢分享了提升沟通力的技巧，刘跃艺分享了大客户销售策略和技巧，彭汉兰分享了高绩效团队建设方法。满满的干货，学员们受益匪浅。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><p></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7f046e1c3.png" title="624f7f046e1c3.png" alt="10.png" width="1012" height="627" style="width: 1012px; height: 627px;"/> &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(120, 172, 254);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; text-indent: 2em;">劳逸结合，身体和灵魂都在路上</strong></span></span></p><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;">课程结束后，人力行政部组织全体学员开展户外健康跑步活动。本次活动由董事长李文帅亲自挂帅，带领大家进行“女子5公里，男子7公里”健康跑活动。除了本次的户外拓展活动，公司还为新来的员工准备了5个运动兴趣小组，新员工可以结合自己兴趣选择合适的运动小组。“身体和灵魂总有一个在路上”，这是精信科技对每一个员工的要求，也是一个人快速成长和进步的“良方”。通过体育锻炼，让新员工更深刻体会公司“要么在学习，要么在锻炼身体，注重综合能力和身体健康双提升”的文化，更快地融入公司团队。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;"><img src="/Uploads/image/20220408624f7f1361a43.png" title="624f7f1361a43.png" alt="11.png" width="974" height="683" style="width: 974px; height: 683px;"/></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px;">本次精英培训圆满落幕，通过本次的培训加深了新员工对公司的了解，同时也提升了新员工对公司的认同感和归属感。“雄关漫道真如铁，而今迈步从头越。”祝愿新伙伴们带着激情和梦想，突破自我，努力前行，携手精信科技，共创伟大公司！</span></section><p></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = null, top = 1, create_id = 12, create_time = '2022-04-08 08:19:25.0', article_time = '2022-04-03 00:00:00.0', status = 0, sort = 1, top_title = '', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 214;
UPDATE jxkj_db.article SET name = '武汉东湖学院南校区信息化建设项目·设备与集成——招标公告', abstract = '武汉东湖学院南校区信息化建设项目·设备与集成公开招标', content = '<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(38,38,38);font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">招标</span></span></strong><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(38,38,38);font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">公告</span></span></strong></h1><h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(38,38,38);font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">一、基本情况</span></span></strong></h2><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">1、项目名称：武汉</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">东湖学院南校区信息化建设项目</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">·设备与集成</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">2、采购方式：公开招标</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋"><img src="/Uploads/image/202204116253c87ed5856.png" title="6253c87ed5856.png" alt="微信图片_20220411141854.png" width="564" height="283" style="width: 564px; height: 283px;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;">3、采购需求简要说明：</span><br/></p><p style="text-indent:32px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px">4</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">、项目地址：湖北嘉鱼（咸宁市嘉鱼县诗经大道与田野大道交汇处）</span></span></p><h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(38,38,38);font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">二、资格要求</span></span></strong></h2><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">1、投标人必须符合以下规定：</span></span></p><p style="text