态宜居新城</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的发展定位，累计投资</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">630</span><span style="font-family:宋体">亿元，实施亿元以上重点项目</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">350</span><span style="font-family:宋体">余个，全面拉开城市发展框架，初步建成了配套完善、动能充沛、风景秀丽、环境优美、民生幸福、活力四射的现代化生态新城。凭借便利的交通条件、完善的基础设施和丰富的政务资源，筑巢引凤，吸引了华强方特、华侨城、新城控股等多家全国一流企业投资</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">落户</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，为新区发展注入了强劲动力。经过多年持续健康发展，太白湖新区进入了蓄势突破、跨越赶超的机遇期、关键期。随着鲁泰大厦、济东数字经济产业园等一批楼宇和园区的投入使用，一个前景更加广阔、未来更加美好的新区发展平台正在形成。现在向各位企业家抛出</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">橄榄枝</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，诚挚邀请李文帅董事长带队到太白湖新区进行实地考察。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">‍</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 17px">&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/image/2023070364a27a8feefab.png" title="64a27a8feefab.png" alt="图片4.png" width="632" height="425" style="width: 632px; height: 425px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 "><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">此次座谈会既是政企的强强联合，更是抢抓机遇、共创辉煌的新起点，希望未来通过多方位、宽领或、深层次的合作，实现双方互惠共赢。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">‍</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', menu_id = 19, file_id = null, top = 1, create_id = 12, create_time = '2023-07-03 15:46:15.0', article_time = '2023-07-02 00:00:00.0', status = 0, sort = 0, top_title = '精准对接 谋求合作 ——济宁市太白湖新区刘昭立主任一行到我司考察调研', clicks = 0 WHERE id = 248;
